72. Saved Section UI: Created a separate "Saved for Later" section in the sidebar.
73. Result Removal: Implemented a "Clear All" button to reset the map and sidebar.
74. One-Click Recall: Added logic to bring a Saved class back into the active map view.
75. Search Input Auto-Format: Created a utility to capitalize and space inputs (cse12 -> CSE 12).
76. Hover Synchronization: Coded map-to-sidebar highlighting for instant visual feedback.
77. Instructor Concatenation: Handled courses with 2+ professors by listing them in the UI.
78. Badge Labels: Added small color badges (Lec, Lab, Dis) inside the map popups.
79. Meta-Tag Configuration: Set up mobile-responsive viewport tags for phone usage.
80. State Management: Developed a global array system to track currentOfferings and markers.

